Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地的聯絡班相繼傳來消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有戰友遭到暗算
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場極度混亂 找不到敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有發動夜襲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有感知系忍者設防
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會發現不了敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是中毒還是其他什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體的狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎都是外傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是物理攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.07,0:00:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只有聯軍忍者被幻術操縱這種可能了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.61,0:00:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 醫療部隊傳來消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的真身是…白絕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是變身為聯軍的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連查克拉都能模仿的忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來在白天的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:01:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸取查克拉的忍者 都能被模仿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的鹿角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方如果無法分辨敵友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拂曉的戰鬥則無法準備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不趕快想出分辨敵人的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間越久 死傷越多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終會演變為友軍間的互相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是白絕的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說白天的戰鬥是夜晚行動的鋪墊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是敵方的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人沒有行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是別大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看守已經加強了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二部隊 岩隱 黑土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了和俘虜交涉而來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我們看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然總用究極藝術感覺有點不值錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也沒辦法 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷遁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知雷遁是自己的弱點 一直提防著…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪達拉 迪達拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 絕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕 是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在以前的交情上來救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了 快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪達拉哥哥 還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音 是黑土嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在以前的交情上來救我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是因為以前的交情被派遣過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來找你幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩隱的審問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥師兜在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道也不說 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是被兜強制復活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆被利用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就忘掉以前的事 給我們一點幫助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜給我展現更加究極藝術的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那宇智波佐助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也被穢土轉生了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助沒死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說蠢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙被我的究極藝術殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥死後 佐助很精神地和雷影戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在是曉的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者聯軍的大敵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙加入曉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助還活著 加入了曉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後我將化為藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前所未有的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將在此地留下前所未有的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我的藝術將會受到前所未有的稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 戰慄吧 驚歎吧 絕望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拗哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的藝術…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…就是爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣怎麼可能沒死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說還活著了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我的究極藝術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的藝術根本沒人知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他驚歎了嗎 恐懼了嗎 絕望了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有慘叫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土遁比雷遁弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的炸彈被雷遁擊中的話就無法引爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的弱點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會總受制於雷遁的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船隊長 總部有急電
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯軍裏混入了敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在不斷進行暗殺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部隊的混亂正在蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們詢問我部的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前為止沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我就如此回復了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才來的那位岩隱女忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為她不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聽嗎 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給個回應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沒完沒了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個打開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遙遠的天邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是河
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些武士…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太單純了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 那些傢伙會吸收查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術就是爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪達拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷遁應該封住了爆遁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那個讓雷遁失效了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼傀儡裏有那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:09:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了還給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虜迪達拉逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同黨絕也在一起 抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的失誤 我一定會負責…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是沮喪的時候 快追
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要逃啊 幹掉他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的起爆黏土已經沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須找個地方補充一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是和以前一樣弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是拖延時間的戰術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來擺脫封印了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:10:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回收了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的究極藝術被全盤否定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不甘心就這麼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經死了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要完成超究極的藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術家的想法真難理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是知識份子還是會讓藝術家發揮一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 我來拖住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 中吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧隱之術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感知到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船隊長 在對面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃到哪去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要黏土 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找土裏有黏土的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你的便吧 迪達拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你更適合自由行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也忙起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在迪達拉哥哥找到起爆黏土之前抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會變麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前幸虧雲隱的重用雷遁壓制了他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在在別的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這支部隊有使用雷遁的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五部隊兵分兩路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這支部隊的主力是武士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:13:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者只負責感知 封印 情報等支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船隊長 我會用雷遁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵來了 迪達拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起爆黏土才這麼點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷遁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地雷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你們妨礙我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電流都被導出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加大雷遁的強度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…已經是我的全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪達拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穢土轉生的身體可是不死之身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上來講 你就是移動的起爆黏土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真俗 絕望了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術是一瞬的閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瞬間就會凋零的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這副身體卻不會凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去尋找超越究極藝術的超究極藝術了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 哥哥那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船大人 在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的地雷炸出的坑成了戰壕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有起爆黏土的迪達拉非常兇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要制定戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能絕緣 雷遁就無法被導出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是這位雷遁忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 就憑我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就專心感知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向總部請求增援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間等待增援了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能使用現有的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我的美學合不來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠍大哥在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定有什麼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快就離去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤獨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但藝術說到底就是孤獨 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地雷埋好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 有什麼靈感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術才沒那麼容易來靈感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更別說超究極的藝術了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 為什麼還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在你眼前的是我 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼬之後是鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不把我放在眼裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪達拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪達拉 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個佐助 好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要讓你戰慄 驚歎 絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你那冷酷的臉扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那裏 在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然比起雷遁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癡迷於藝術才是哥哥的弱點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑土
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們打算幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然沒爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑這種刀沒法阻止我的藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士竟然會雷遁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是雷遁 是蓄電池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來很管用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶都是岩石啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀穿透不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算穿透了 雷遁也不會被導出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 放開我 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的佐助在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋黑土
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別小看我啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然假扮成佐助 真是像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我從迪達拉哥哥嘴裏套不出線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一點都不配合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持之前的戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向總部報告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 把那個還給我才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再添麻煩了哦 迪達拉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超究極藝術的主題決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏露臉也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術永遠不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我死了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,忍者們參加第四次忍界大戰的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,我們要如何保護村子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.31,0:22:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,這次大戰 敵人很有可能來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.01,0:22:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,那種小嘍啰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,迄今為止打跑過好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,木葉的老闆娘們可不能讓人小瞧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,媽媽聯軍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,保護村子也是很重要的
